transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Yes.
Executive: Ya Tirupati Agro product se baat kar rahe hain Shekhar ji?
Customer: Nahi aap kaun bol rahe ho?
Executive: Ah main Vijay bol raha tha India Mart se.
Customer: Pata nahi.
Executive: Ah ye Shekhar sir se baat karna tha sir ek baar.
Customer: Haan bataiye main us hisab se baat karaunga na sir se.
Executive: Ah main sir Vijay bol raha tha India Mart se baat kar raha tha service ke regarding call kiya tha maine.
Customer: Sir abhi nahi hai.
summary:

- Executive wanted to speak with Shekhar regarding service from India Mart.



Resolution:

- Executive stated he was Vijay from India Mart calling about service.



Next Steps:
